  "page": "Battle Beneath the Gods Eye",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the battle between Aemond and Daemon Targaryen, see <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_Above_the_Gods_Eye\" title=\"Battle Above the Gods Eye\">Battle Above the Gods Eye</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle Beneath the Gods Eye</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Battle_Beneath_the_Gods_Eye.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Battle Beneath the Gods Eye.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/68/Battle_Beneath_the_Gods_Eye.jpg/350px-Battle_Beneath_the_Gods_Eye.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"234\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/68/Battle_Beneath_the_Gods_Eye.jpg/525px-Battle_Beneath_the_Gods_Eye.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/68/Battle_Beneath_the_Gods_Eye.jpg/700px-Battle_Beneath_the_Gods_Eye.jpg 2x\" /></a><div><div style=\"width:100%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a> make short work of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Aenys I)\">Aegon the Uncrowned</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Quicksilver\" title=\"Quicksilver\">Quicksilver</a> during the Battle Beneath the Gods Eye, as depicted by Michael Komarck in <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>.</div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_the_Uncrowned%27s_rebellion\" title=\"Aegon the Uncrowned&#39;s rebellion\">Aegon the Uncrowned's rebellion<